cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to predict a business rating based on user-generated reviews texts alone. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also involves feature generation and machine learning models, which makes cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves the use of bag of words and Part-of-Speech analysis, which are common techniques in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CY (Computers and Society) sub-categories.
